title: Seed to Leaf Organics
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Pizza, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out, Fusion
description: Est. 2015 in downtown serveing breakfast, lunch, and early dinner with a combination of cooked and raw dishes. Sample dishes such as raw tacos and pizzette, buffalo cauliflower, air fries, pulled jackfruit sandwich, walnut veggie burger, bean and grain dishes, gluten-free bread with avocado, acai bowls, coconut yogurt parfait. Uses gluten-free, non-gmo ingredients. Contemporary atmosphere with a long wooden bar as well seating at tables.
